data.description: Take a look at this amazing El Camino home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, close to schools, parks, shopping and more. This home features 4 bedrooms, plus a 25'x23' hobby room/workout room- sky's the limit on this one. The living room is inviting and cozy. The family room has a wood burning fireplace that makes it great for relaxing or entertaining. The kitchen has tons of cabinets and counterspace making it a chef's dream kitchen. Many cabinets and beautiful built-in wood shelving throughout the home. The 4th non-conforming bedroom on the lower level can be an office or den.  The master suite has a steam shower – helpful after a long day. Some nice landscaping front and back from mature trees, flowers and raised garden beds.  Solar to keep electrical bills down and the best part they are paid off. RV or boat parking on side of home so plenty of room to store your toys.  And if all that wasn't enough you have a hot tub to enjoy the amazing mountain views from the backyard sanctuary. Schedule your showing today!  The yearly HOA is optional $20 per year. For more information visit https://elcaminohomeowners.org/
